author: Journal Inquirer Staff
title: Ellington remains undefeated
text:
Ellington remains undefeated By Journal Inquirer Staff Journal Inquirer | 0 comments 
It may be early in the season, but the Ellington High football team has already has its designs on an undefeated season. 
The Purple Knights’ high-powered offense was able to take advantage of Stafford turnovers to wear down their scrappy opponents and pull away late to earn a 40-7 conference road victory on Friday night.
